description: These emotes are all touching various different things in various different ways. They are giving pokes and prods the objects out of affection as well as disgust. Whatever emotions their faces display tells us how they feel about the object they are poking. Some of these emotes are poking other people while others are poking the air, waiting for you to add in another object for them to poke.
